Application contains use of MVVM architecture along with retrofit to parse the news data
Application for basic news UI with use of MVVM and retofit as of now. Will be adding Koin for dependency injection and Kotest framework for writing unit test

References :
1. https://howtodoandroid.com/mvvm-retrofit-recyclerview-kotlin/
2. https://developer.android.com/codelabs/android-databinding#6

Koin Dependency Injection reference link for learning and implementation :
1. https://kotest.io/docs/quickstart
2. https://insert-koin.io/docs/quickstart/android-viewmodel
3. https://insert-koin.io/docs/reference/koin-android/viewmodel/
4. https://medium.com/swlh/mvvm-on-android-with-the-architecture-components-koin-f53c3c200363
5. https://medium.com/swlh/dependency-injection-with-koin-6b6364dc8dba
6. https://en.proft.me/2016/12/28/getting-started-dependency-injection-android-using/
